casebody.data:
No. 126,

Orig.

Kansas v. Nebraska et al.

Motion of the Special Master for allowance of fee and disbursements granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $152,563.19 for the period August 1, 2000, through February 28, 2001, to be paid evenly by Kansas, Nebraska, and Colorado. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 531 U. S. 806.]
